Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.redblacktree

Class RedBlackTree

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.redblacktree.AbstractRedBlackTree
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.redblacktree.RedBlackTree
All Implemented Interfaces:
BaseOpsInt, TreeOpsInt, TreeTraversalOps
public class RedBlackTree extends AbstractRedBlackTree

Title: RedBlackTree

Description:

Int implementation for an Red Black tree. Note that a Red Black Tree tree is a self-balancing tree which checks the colors of the nodes in the subtrees to ensure equal distancing of nodes and minimal search time
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
